                  <msItemStruct>
                     <note type="general">Text is written on both sides: Side 1 (Recto) is 4 lines, Side 2 (Verso) is 6 lines.  Heavy, short script with some Kufic characters. Diacritical markings expressed by strokes, points with red dots. Suras 40 and 41 separated by ornamentation. (Della Vida)</note>
                     <note type="local_note">Museum of Archaeology and Anthropology, Ellen W. Harrison Collection</note>
