                  </msItemStruct>
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
                  <objectDesc>
                     <supportDesc>
                        <support>25.2 x 13.5cm. Thin parchment, originally white, at present dingy brown. Upper part of a sheet written on both faces.  Width is fully preserved.  Upper margin and lower side are damaged.  Last three lines of the six lines on the verso are entirely faded out.</support>
